00:19:28,520 --> 00:19:29,560
we'll do it daily.

300
00:19:30,553 --> 00:19:31,593
Okay, Dr. Fang.

301
00:19:32,880 --> 00:19:33,880
You know,

302
00:19:34,680 --> 00:19:35,680
Linlin isn't here.

303
00:19:36,720 --> 00:19:37,720
When I'm alone,

304
00:19:38,920 --> 00:19:39,920
I'm scared.

305
00:19:49,920 --> 00:19:51,280
How did you feel after going home?

306
00:19:53,160 --> 00:19:54,160
I felt...

307
00:19:55,146 --> 00:19:56,586
I wasn't alone anymore.

308
00:20:01,360 --> 00:20:02,360
Being able to say it

309
00:20:02,880 --> 00:20:03,880
felt like a relief.

310
00:20:09,800 --> 00:20:11,040
I used to think,

311
00:20:12,640 --> 00:20:13,880
if anyone found out,

312
00:20:14,280 --> 00:20:15,280
I'd kill myself.

313
00:20:16,880 --> 00:20:18,120
But now that you know,

314
00:20:19,760 --> 00:20:21,480
I feel alive again.

315
00:20:23,926 --> 00:20:25,166
You said you had nightmares.

316
00:20:26,360 --> 00:20:27,560
Let's talk about them.

317
00:20:31,306 --> 00:20:32,306
Dreams?

318
00:20:33,680 --> 00:20:35,280
They're always about that.

319
00:20:36,560 --> 00:20:37,640
Is it always him?

320
00:20:39,400 --> 00:20:40,400
Or

321
00:20:41,320 --> 00:20:42,560
is there someone else?

322
00:20:45,400 --> 00:20:47,280
You just called my name.

323
00:20:50,560 --> 00:20:51,560
Fang Chi.

324
00:20:53,240 --> 00:20:54,240
Fang Chi.

325
00:20:58,000 --> 00:20:59,000
Besides me.

326
00:21:04,119 --> 00:21:05,119
No.

327
00:21:09,280 --> 00:21:10,520
You seem nervous.

328
00:21:12,926 --> 00:21:13,926
I...

329
00:21:15,040 --> 00:21:16,040
I...

330
00:21:16,840 --> 00:21:17,960
Don't lie to me.

331
00:21:20,600 --> 00:21:21,840
Do you want the paddle?

332
00:21:22,360 --> 00:21:23,360
I was wrong.

333
00:21:25,280 --> 00:21:26,280
Only once.

334
00:21:27,760 --> 00:21:28,760
Only once, it was.

335
00:21:31,400 --> 00:21:32,400
Justin.

336
00:21:33,480 --> 00:21:34,480
Why him?

337
00:21:36,240 --> 00:21:37,400
There was an auction before.

338
00:21:38,520 --> 00:21:39,520
He got drunk at dinner.

339
00:21:40,440 --> 00:21:41,440
On the way back,

340
00:21:43,720 --> 00:21:44,440
he tried to grab me.

341
00:21:44,520 --> 00:21:45,520
I dodged him.

342
00:21:46,480 --> 00:21:47,480
That night,

343
00:21:48,320 --> 00:21:49,320
I had a nightmare.

344
00:21:50,640 --> 00:21:51,760
In the dream, I fought back.

345
00:21:52,520 --> 00:21:53,760
But he didn't let me go.

346
00:21:55,080 --> 00:21:56,480
Did you feel pleasure in the dream?

347
00:21:58,080 --> 00:21:59,120
Not with them.

348
00:22:04,160 --> 00:22:05,160
In my dreams,

349
00:22:07,000 --> 00:22:08,000
only with you.

350
00:22:10,160 --> 00:22:11,200
I only feel it with you.

351
00:22:13,593 --> 00:22:14,713
Because I want it.

352
00:22:16,000 --> 00:22:17,000
What?

353
00:22:17,080 --> 00:22:18,080
Want it or not...

354
00:22:19,840 --> 00:22:20,840
Sorry.

355
00:22:21,200 --> 00:22:22,200
I tainted you.

356
00:22:23,560 --> 00:22:24,560
I'm shameless.

357
00:22:25,000 --> 00:22:26,000
I'm sick.

358
00:22:28,880 --> 00:22:30,600
But when I see your face,

359
00:22:32,000 --> 00:22:33,000
I just...

360
00:22:33,800 --> 00:22:34,800
Go on.

361
00:22:35,960 --> 00:22:36,960
I want to hear it.

362
00:22:38,760 --> 00:22:40,240
At first, I couldn't believe it.

363
00:22:41,840 --> 00:22:43,680
Until I touched your face.

364
00:22:44,800 --> 00:22:45,800
Even if it was a dream,

365
00:22:47,833 --> 00:22:49,073
I just wanted to hold you

366
00:22:50,920 --> 00:22:51,920
and cry on your shoulder.

367
00:22:54,800 --> 00:22:55,800
Why cry?

368
00:22:59,120 --> 00:23:00,120
Because

369
00:23:03,920 --> 00:23:05,280
you finally came to save me.

370
00:23:34,680 --> 00:23:35,440
I'm glad

371
00:23:35,640 --> 00:23:36,720
you dared to ride in a car.

372
00:23:38,520 --> 00:23:40,280
Because you were in the car.

373
00:23:42,560 --> 00:23:43,560
Want me to walk you up?

374
00:23:44,560 --> 00:23:45,560
No.

375
00:23:46,913 --> 00:23:48,273
If you're nearby later,

376
00:23:49,560 --> 00:23:51,120
come by for coffee anytime.

377
00:23:51,800 --> 00:23:53,040
Wouldn't that trouble you?

378
00:23:53,320 --> 00:23:54,320
Not at all.

379
00:23:58,736 --> 00:23:59,976
I'd love you to come.

380
00:24:00,000 --> 00:24:00,400
What?

381
00:24:01,240 --> 00:24:02,240
Nothing.

382
00:24:03,920 --> 00:24:04,920
Dr. Fang.

383
00:24:06,040 --> 00:24:07,040
See you next time.

384
00:25:22,360 --> 00:25:23,720
Hello. Do you have an appointment?

385
00:25:24,080 --> 00:25:25,320
I'm Mr. Gao Zhun's friend.

386
00:25:26,480 --> 00:25:27,600
He left something in my car.

387
00:25:28,040 --> 00:25:29,040
One moment, please.

388
00:25:35,280 --> 00:25:36,400
Mr. Gao isn't answering.

389
00:25:36,960 --> 00:25:37,440
I understand.

390
00:25:37,840 --> 00:25:38,840
I'll wait here.

391
00:25:38,960 --> 00:25:40,720
Why don't you sit inside?

392
00:25:41,160 --> 00:25:42,160
This way.

393
00:25:42,320 --> 00:25:45,040
Mr. Gao and Mr. Jia are in a meeting.

394
00:25:45,360 --> 00:25:46,440
Once they're done,

395
00:25:46,480 --> 00:25:47,680
I'll let you know right away.

396
00:25:47,960 --> 00:25:48,960
Please.

397
00:25:51,160 --> 00:25:52,200
I want

398
00:25:53,960 --> 00:25:55,040
to find a chance...

399
00:25:56,066 --> 00:25:57,346
to stop him.

400
00:26:00,960 --> 00:26:03,040
Is the Mr. Jia meeting with Mr. Gao

401
00:26:03,720 --> 00:26:04,720
this man?

402
00:26:04,960 --> 00:26:05,320
Yes.

403
00:26:05,560 --> 00:26:06,656
Mr. Jia is with our company.

404
00:26:06,680 --> 00:26:07,680
Where are they meeting?

405
00:26:08,600 --> 00:26:09,760
The eighth-floor conference room.

406
00:26:10,440 --> 00:26:11,920
Sir, what are you doing?

407
00:26:26,520 --> 00:26:27,240
Where's the conference room?

408
00:26:27,480 --> 00:26:28,480
Over there.

409
00:26:44,840 --> 00:26:45,840
Dr. Fang.

410
00:26:47,800 --> 00:26:49,040
What are you...

411
00:26:52,720 --> 00:26:53,720
Come with me.

412
00:26:58,200 --> 00:26:59,200
What's going on?

413
00:27:06,520 --> 00:27:07,520
Continue the meeting.

414
00:27:15,320 --> 00:27:16,560
Why didn't you answer my calls?

415
00:27:17,520 --> 00:27:18,520
I was in a meeting.

416
00:27:18,720 --> 00:27:19,960
My phone was on silent.

417
00:27:46,320 --> 00:27:47,320
Are you free today?

418
00:27:48,720 --> 00:27:49,720
Yes.

419
00:27:50,086 --> 00:27:51,846
If it's for you, I'm free whenever.

420
00:27:54,560 --> 00:27:55,560
Then come with me.

421
00:27:58,040 --> 00:27:59,040
I just remembered.

422
00:28:00,480 --> 00:28:01,720
You still need one test.

423
00:28:06,840 --> 00:28:07,840
Okay.

424
00:28:09,720 --> 00:28:10,720
Dr. Fang.

425
00:28:11,720 --> 00:28:12,720
I'm happy

426
00:28:13,600 --> 00:28:14,640
you came for me.

427
00:28:35,360 --> 00:28:36,360
Don't be afraid.

428
00:28:37,720 --> 00:28:38,720
I'm with you.

429
00:28:42,080 --> 00:28:43,080
If I really have it,

430
00:28:46,040 --> 00:28:47,040
leave me.

431
00:28:49,320 --> 00:28:50,320
Let me die.

432
00:28:54,160 --> 00:28:55,160
You'll be okay.

433
00:28:56,320 --> 00:28:56,680
My God.

434
00:28:56,760 --> 00:28:58,480
Two men holding hands.

435
00:29:02,800 --> 00:29:03,880
Don't mind what they think.

436
00:29:05,640 --> 00:29:07,120
I only care how you feel.

437
00:29:24,840 --> 00:29:25,840
Just a second.

438
00:29:27,600 --> 00:29:28,600
It won't hurt much.

439
00:29:39,000 --> 00:29:40,000
Press and hold.

440
00:29:41,560 --> 00:29:41,800
I...

441
00:29:41,880 --> 00:29:42,880
I can do it myself.

442
00:29:44,800 --> 00:29:45,800
It will bleed.

443
00:29:46,360 --> 00:29:47,360
What if...

444
00:29:47,840 --> 00:29:48,840
Your hand.

445
00:29:49,120 --> 00:29:50,120
Give it to me.

446
00:30:04,240 --> 00:30:05,240
Don't worry.

447
00:30:05,720 --> 00:30:07,200
I'll stay with you no matter what.

448
00:30:11,240 --> 00:30:12,240
I'll get the report.

449
00:30:15,520 --> 00:30:17,200
Your boyfriend is so sweet.

450
00:30:19,680 --> 00:30:20,680
He's not my boyfriend.

451
00:30:23,000 --> 00:30:24,000
He's not.

452
00:30:24,720 --> 00:30:25,720
He's my doctor.

453
00:30:26,400 --> 00:30:27,400
Doctor?

454
00:30:28,033 --> 00:30:29,513
The kind who gives shots at night?

455
00:30:40,080 --> 00:30:41,080
What's wrong?

456
00:30:41,320 --> 00:30:42,320
Scared?

457
00:30:43,360 --> 00:30:44,360
You're a doctor?

458
00:30:45,400 --> 00:30:46,400
Yes.

459
00:30:46,760 --> 00:30:47,760
A therapist.

460
00:30:48,160 --> 00:30:48,680
Oh.

461
00:30:49,336 --> 00:30:50,496
Then mental issues...

462
00:30:50,793 --> 00:30:51,793
can I come to you too?

463
00:30:52,280 --> 00:30:53,320
I often can't sleep.

464
00:30:53,400 --> 00:30:54,400
And I have nightmares.

465
00:30:54,480 --> 00:30:55,760
I don't know what to do.

466
00:30:56,560 --> 00:30:57,760
You can come in for therapy.

467
00:30:58,920 --> 00:30:59,960
The first session is free.

468
00:31:00,706 --> 00:31:02,346
Can I have your number?

469
00:31:08,840 --> 00:31:10,120
Call me if you need therapy.

470
00:31:11,120 --> 00:31:12,120
Okay.

471
00:31:14,680 --> 00:31:15,680
But

472
00:31:16,586 --> 00:31:17,826
when you need help,

473
00:31:18,000 --> 00:31:19,000
you can call me.

474
00:31:20,920 --> 00:31:22,120
Even at 3 a.m.

475
00:31:28,800 --> 00:31:29,800
What's wrong?

476
00:31:30,800 --> 00:31:31,800
Mr. Gao.

477
00:31:32,840 --> 00:31:33,840
Gao Zhun.

478
00:31:34,480 --> 00:31:35,720
Look at me.

479
00:31:36,440 --> 00:31:37,680
Aw, having a fight?

480
00:31:42,640 --> 00:31:43,920
Did those people say something?

481
00:31:45,760 --> 00:31:47,520
Are you afraid they'll think we're together?

482
00:31:53,953 --> 00:31:55,153
They all came alone.

483
00:31:56,080 --> 00:31:57,080
Their so-called friends,

484
00:31:57,360 --> 00:31:58,360
bed partners,

485
00:31:58,560 --> 00:31:59,560
none of them came.

486
00:32:01,080 --> 00:32:02,080
But you have me.

487
00:32:04,000 --> 00:32:05,120
So they're jealous.

488
00:32:06,720 --> 00:32:07,720
Don't overthink it.

489
00:32:09,240 --> 00:32:10,240
Understand?

490
00:32:14,080 --> 00:32:15,080
Then are we...

491
00:32:21,120 --> 00:32:22,560
You're safe.

492
00:32:30,920 --> 00:32:31,920
It's okay.

493
00:32:42,800 --> 00:32:43,800
Thank you.

494
00:32:44,760 --> 00:32:45,760
Fang...

495
00:32:48,440 --> 00:32:49,440
Doctor Fang.

496
00:33:08,560 --> 00:33:11,040
Are you afraid they'll think we're together?

497
00:33:14,240 --> 00:33:15,680
If you need help,

498
00:33:15,800 --> 00:33:17,080
you can call me too.

499
00:33:18,680 --> 00:33:19,680
Call?

500
00:33:21,760 --> 00:33:22,760
I can call.

501
00:33:23,600 --> 00:33:24,800
Others can call too.

502
00:33:27,280 --> 00:33:28,440
Anyone can call.

503
00:33:29,240 --> 00:33:30,440
Anyone can call.

504
00:33:32,080 --> 00:33:34,200
I'm not afraid they'll misunderstand us.

505
00:33:35,280 --> 00:33:36,280
I'm just afraid.

506
00:33:37,000 --> 00:33:38,000
Afraid

507
00:33:39,520 --> 00:33:40,520
that once I get better,

508
00:33:43,320 --> 00:33:44,800
we won't be connected anymore.

509
00:34:20,120 --> 00:34:21,120
Mr. Gao.

510
00:34:21,960 --> 00:34:24,760
Writing to patients
is part of narrative therapy.

511
00:34:26,440 --> 00:34:27,440
When I write to others,

512
00:34:27,840 --> 00:34:30,000
I usually recap our sessions.

513
00:34:31,760 --> 00:34:33,120
But this letter is for you.

514
00:34:34,640 --> 00:34:35,680
I want it to be different.

515
00:34:37,920 --> 00:34:38,920
Mr. Gao.

516
00:34:39,880 --> 00:34:41,800
Want to know how I see you?

517
00:34:43,240 --> 00:34:44,400
Remember the exhibition?

518
00:34:45,000 --> 00:34:46,240
You waited for me in the dark.

519
00:34:47,880 --> 00:34:48,880
It's me.

520
00:34:50,600 --> 00:34:52,600
Remember those touch exercises?

521
00:34:53,360 --> 00:34:54,560
You were terrified,

522
00:34:55,040 --> 00:34:56,040
but you didn't run.

523
00:34:57,600 --> 00:34:58,600
Don't be afraid.

524
00:34:59,600 --> 00:35:00,600
It's okay.

525
00:35:01,480 --> 00:35:03,880
Remember the Qixi fireworks and fountain?

526
00:35:04,240 --> 00:35:06,800
You bravely shared your story with me.

527
00:35:07,920 --> 00:35:09,640
What struck me deepest

528
00:35:10,480 --> 00:35:12,600
was your courage at the edge.

529
00:35:14,120 --> 00:35:15,120
And your beauty.

530
00:35:17,200 --> 00:35:19,600
Maybe beauty is an odd word for a man.

531
00:35:20,920 --> 00:35:22,120
But you are beautiful.

532
00:35:22,920 --> 00:35:25,720
Beautiful flowers are the ones people break.

533
00:35:27,640 --> 00:35:29,360
Beauty brought you pain.

534
00:35:30,240 --> 00:35:31,360
But you should know

535
00:35:32,120 --> 00:35:33,280
beauty is not your fault.

536
00:35:35,640 --> 00:35:37,200
What hurts me most

537
00:35:37,640 --> 00:35:39,960
is seeing you punish yourself
for another man's sin.

538
00:35:41,480 --> 00:35:44,040
What scares me most is
hearing you talk about death.

539
00:35:46,880 --> 00:35:47,880
Lastly,

540
00:35:49,200 --> 00:35:51,600
thank you for trusting me.

541
00:35:53,000 --> 00:35:54,880
No matter how far I pushed,

542
00:35:55,760 --> 00:35:57,760
you always gave in to me.

543
00:35:59,200 --> 00:36:00,960
More than once, I felt

544
00:36:01,720 --> 00:36:02,720
knowing you

545
00:36:03,000 --> 00:36:05,560
was one of the greatest gifts of my life.

546
00:36:07,600 --> 00:36:08,600
Thank you.

547
00:36:09,680 --> 00:36:10,680
Gao Zhun.

548
00:36:50,706 --> 00:36:53,619
[Gao Zhun calling]

549
00:36:58,880 --> 00:36:59,880
Mr. Gao.

550
00:37:00,600 --> 00:37:01,600
It's late.

551
00:37:03,120 --> 00:37:04,120
What is it?

552
00:37:07,360 --> 00:37:08,360
The letter.

553
00:37:08,920 --> 00:37:09,920
I got it.

554
00:37:12,120 --> 00:37:13,120
I'm sorry.

555
00:37:14,560 --> 00:37:15,640
I shouldn't have acted up.

556
00:37:17,400 --> 00:37:18,400
Why did you?

557
00:37:19,440 --> 00:37:20,440
I just...

558
00:37:24,960 --> 00:37:26,960
I couldn't stand you giving
that boy your card.

559
00:37:28,600 --> 00:37:30,920
I couldn't stand you being as
kind to him as you are to me.

560
00:37:33,440 --> 00:37:35,200
I want you to be kind only to me.

561
00:37:37,480 --> 00:37:38,840
I only want you to look at me.

562
00:37:41,480 --> 00:37:42,480
I...

563
00:37:47,640 --> 00:37:48,640
I get jealous.

564
00:41:39,320 --> 00:41:40,320
Mr. Jia.

565
00:41:40,440 --> 00:41:41,440
Please calm down.

566
00:41:43,960 --> 00:41:45,200
As you can see,

567
00:41:46,000 --> 00:41:47,120
I wasn't looking for you.

568
00:41:49,760 --> 00:41:50,760
Yes.

569
00:41:51,000 --> 00:41:52,000
It was a coincidence.

570
00:41:54,200 --> 00:41:55,200
Don't worry.

571
00:41:58,040 --> 00:41:59,040
I'm a doctor.

572
00:41:59,840 --> 00:42:01,920
My ethics require me
to protect client privacy.

573
00:42:04,480 --> 00:42:05,480
Yes.

574
00:42:06,080 --> 00:42:07,080
He doesn't know

575
00:42:07,760 --> 00:42:08,920
you're my client.
